{
  "stem": "10588.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she looked at me and she said, 'Go, go, Itkele.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "God is in the root cellar too.' And she said she'll wait for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She lit a candle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She gave me the candle to go down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the root cellar was dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It had a dirt floor, no windows, a long ladder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "To go down-- it was in the kitchen-- you had to-- and an iron ring, it was a square cut out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You would have to pull up the ring, you know, the square, and to walk down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And somehow, my mother's reassurance, and having the candle, and mostly, she said, 'Go, go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "God's in the root cellar too.' I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For some reason, it gave me the courage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It diminished my fear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I went down, and I brought up the butter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And after that, I was not so afraid anymore to go down to the root cellar, because I was always-- my mother-- the echo of my mother's voice was still in my head. 'Go, go, Itkele.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "God is in the root cellar.' In fact, during concentration camp, I was often thinking about this comment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was thinking, when I was in Poland, we didn't have electricity.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But neither did we have electric charge wires when we were fenced in and couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So-- and then, also, there was, for instance, Passover I remember very much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "For one thing, I was born during Passover, you know, the Jewish holiday celebrating freedom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I remember Passover was very beautiful in our home, because we had a large-- lots of relatives.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My aunt and uncle had seven children, and they had already grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the relatives would used to go together.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
